{"type": "article", "id": 29716, "title": "索尼耳机线打造的配件", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T11:55:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160717205707acDenM5s0oNHIxq4.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>还记得上周我们介绍过<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29581.html\">利用飞机座椅布料</a>制作的时尚配件吗？今天的这组名为 Fashion Unplugged 的配件在原素材和成品之间的跨度上可能还要大一点：它由索尼与注重可持续发展的泳装品牌 Auria 共同打造，是为了庆祝索尼无线耳机 h.ear 上市而设计的。共计超过 113 米长的耳机线同护照套、太阳眼镜盒、沙滩包、手机壳以及沙滩拖鞋组合在了一起，五款产品的颜色也分别对应了耳机的五种配色，鲜艳明亮很有夏天的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717205730GsMYfxi6uBrvQq1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717205731FXwQBZsluKEpkHOD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717205731tKigeE7rVvn3IuHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717205731WhtnOiJvUD32dQfe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}